                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4912,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_4293187669096717509.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Набу Маликата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Jinn are Nabi Malikata's familiars.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4911,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_2834910047270303942.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Аль-Ахмар",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "After Nabu Malikata's death, Al-Ahmar promised the Jinn their mistress was destined to awake someday, so they began serving him.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ay-Khanoum",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"City of the Moon Maiden,\" that was build by Nabu Malikata and Al-Ahmar for the Jinn.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Gurabad",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A city that rose and fell under the influence of the Mother of the Jinn, Liloupar.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ormazd",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A shepherd who became a ruler of Gurabad under Liloupar's influence.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Shirin",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kisra Parvezravan",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Liloupar's children",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Shiruyeh",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Liloupar's grandson, Shirin and Kisra's son, who was the reason for a calamity called \"Shiruyeh's Plague.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Notable Jinn",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3530,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/06/237301566/919fe68dc22d6d80b3a8118ce6c80491_7611509035816815714.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Лилупар",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Mother of the Jinn gave powers to Ormazd to rule Gurabad and led to its fall.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ferigees",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The guardian of the City of the Moon Maiden and the Mother of the Jinn who became a seal on the Eternal Oasis.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
